{"tid":248093,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人去過小琉球","createTime":"2017-05-18T09:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T12:59:51.000Z","uid":104462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12699f45ec0c064831ff05d0b44ade41ea7d225d","tid":248093,"uid":104462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"最近發生生d事 想一個人去下旅行散下心<br />\n因為自己本身都鍾意大自然<br />\n想問下有無巴絲去過台灣小琉球？<br />\n有無咩評價同埋去幾多日先夠？<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097aa091a002c34326b5e02cc7785f27a929b196","tid":248093,"uid":104462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh"},{"pid":"8b9b8280d92d39af3071e660db597b91a697e5f8","tid":248093,"uid":14535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T15:46:16.000Z","msg":"小琉好細 可以租電動電單車/ 汽油電單車代步<br />\n去最起馬要玩浮潛，夠膽又有時間玩埋深潛<br />\n島上面無銀聯機 要帶夠錢入去<br />\n成個島得兩間7-11<br />\n啲所謂景點 乜野烏鬼洞之煩其實無乜特別<br />\n唔建議一個人去 最好最少兩個人齊去<br />\n其實好似香港嘅長洲 要快一兩日可以做哂無想做嘅野<br />\n有咩想知再問"},{"pid":"d830b0218187d60983a1c0509f46a3e49c708192","tid":248093,"uid":14535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T15:56:25.000Z","msg":"其實唔潛係海邊都會見到海龜<br />\n島上面有自助洗衣機<br />\n民宿住過三間<br />\n夢幻漁村(近海)，珊瑚假期(近大街)，夏提(近唔近碼頭間7-11)<br />\n全島有兩個碼頭 一個係公營船 一個民營船<br />\n民營船好似快少少同密啲<br />\n近民營船個度有條大街 大部份鋪頭包括食都係哂個頭<br />\n小琉球好似有隻叫相思麵 淨係開半日 上次去就唔到時間到走都食唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/235127_d2a00cc49b9a820c0b189af180de3f72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F235127_d2a00cc49b9a820c0b189af180de3f72.jpg&h=8696e962&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/235129_03477f48f62ec61cb488192c2621295c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F235129_03477f48f62ec61cb488192c2621295c.jpg&h=aa4987e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/235129_284d5503f4d1d03d0d2f49aabd1d1659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F235129_284d5503f4d1d03d0d2f49aabd1d1659.jpg&h=ef8a7bfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84719fcaf9f8d727b61659c79f2c9eb61e238a6f","tid":248093,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:07:51.000Z","msg":"去過浮潛<br />\n<br />\n少人好多 成個環境都好清靜<br />\n<br />\n成個島d人大家都識哂咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9c7043ae6624c641a0a8ab071dfbf489e2d588","tid":248093,"uid":35228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"去學O仔好抵屌 乜柒都包哂都係3000左右<br />\n講緊係島上既所有活動"},{"pid":"a31dd821d5a3bcdbf1aeb5518861c7fedc5069c3","tid":248093,"uid":18272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:21:51.000Z","msg":"去埋潛水果d就兩日，唔玩水上活動既話真係一日就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ～～租埋電動車一個鐘唔洗都環完個島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885bb9f10c0cacace264f19721eed3067824bf89","tid":248093,"uid":14535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去埋潛水果d就兩日，唔玩水上活動既話真係一日就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ～～租埋電動車一個鐘唔洗都環完個島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夜晚行汽油車我朋友15-20 分鐘一圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係講緊廿幾分鍾就一圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70992da67b7919b12c38c8847b64aefd7c7ab886","tid":248093,"uid":104462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T17:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小琉好細 可以租電動電單車/ 汽油電單車代步<br />\n去最起馬要玩浮潛，夠膽又有時間玩埋深潛<br />\n島上面無銀聯機 要帶夠錢入去<br />\n成個島得兩間7-11<br />\n啲所謂景點 乜野烏鬼洞之煩其實無乜特別<br />\n唔建議一個人去 最好最少兩個人齊去<br />\n其實好似香港嘅長洲 要快一兩日可以做哂無想做嘅野<br />\n有咩想知再問</blockquote><br />\n想問下巴打點解唔建議兩個人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係因為d活動唔岩一個人玩？"},{"pid":"806d9192b43bd494472f20c5904c6a2ab8a386c5","tid":248093,"uid":104462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T17:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去學O仔好抵屌 乜柒都包哂都係3000左右<br />\n講緊係島上既所有活動</blockquote><br />\n巴打Total Spend左幾耐時間？"},{"pid":"9527cfe36acdc96c841d000035b2a4fb729a4bc8","tid":248093,"uid":104462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過浮潛<br />\n<br />\n少人好多 成個環境都好清靜<br />\n<br />\n成個島d人大家都識哂咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個到其實多唔多遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4026b39ba56bb1f8350a48c0fb6ea0942a1f0e","tid":248093,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T17:19:39.000Z","msg":"好細 但你話散心唔玩水上活動就一流<br />\n如果你鐘意海, 可以坐下海邊睇下海龜咁就一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定要租電單車 / 電動車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩浮潛既話我覺得美人洞有d伏 雖然都可以同海龜一齊游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但花瓶岩浮潛會靚過美人洞 但唔好掂d海龜 受保護架<br />\n<br />\n其他景點都幾無謂, 不過成日流流長又有電單車去下都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n租民宿可以租d套票 有包船飛果d, 仲可以去埋潮間帶 好多好得意既生物野睇<br />\n但去之前一定要洗乾淨手, 有d生物可以摸佢, 但唔好留底化學野係隻野到<br />\n<br />\n同埋一定一定要防曬 如果唔係會曬撚到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a21accf5112cd38dd51e9ff750d6ff6352bd8e8","tid":248093,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T17:21:34.000Z","msg":"依家係墾丁，過幾日都會去小琉球玩一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b06b79ee830eeb9f40a19abfadb881e986424c5","tid":248093,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T17:27:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好細 但你話散心唔玩水上活動就一流<br />\n如果你鐘意海, 可以坐下海邊睇下海龜咁就一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定要租電單車 / 電動車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩浮潛既話我覺得美人洞有d伏 雖然都可以同海龜一齊游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但花瓶岩浮潛會靚過美人洞 但唔好掂d海龜 受保護架<br />\n<br />\n其他景點都幾無謂, 不過成日流流長又有電單車去下都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n租民宿可以租d套票 有包船飛果d, 仲可以去埋潮間帶 好多好得意既生物野睇<br />\n但去之前一定要洗乾淨手, 有d生物可以摸佢, 但唔好留底化學野係隻野到<br />\n<br />\n同埋一定一定要防曬 如果唔係會曬撚到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/SXoFNK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FSXoFNK.jpg&h=f50fefe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/bWHxjr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FbWHxjr.jpg&h=c176f71a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/tmHKEG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FtmHKEG.jpg&h=382b7928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/kJ78LR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FkJ78LR.jpg&h=2fa9290a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有圖有計傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eff75361f6598ec81f86ba1332eb52aa48f8a79","tid":248093,"uid":1024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T18:02:45.000Z","msg":"電動車洗唔洗車牌？"},{"pid":"b812e5225aff96554bf18b5c2cd121b53e378aef","tid":248093,"uid":5394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T19:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電動車洗唔洗車牌？</blockquote><br />\n唔使<br />\n<br />\n有兩隻電動車<br />\n揸唔掂電動車就揸電動單車<br />\n不過好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夜晚跟導賞團去夜遊同睇星<br />\n成班人飛車好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2579ea22b642292e55e36bc8a472bb871f418c","tid":248093,"uid":21821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21bf72dd2ac18416cfc74906d67515a134274a3d","tid":248093,"uid":21821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:02:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上一次去<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/19/130202_a08584ab5415d7ee42b9f8b6b3f09ce8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2F130202_a08584ab5415d7ee42b9f8b6b3f09ce8.jpg&h=3b65cd73&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/19/130203_e1dd0d9b33637f4709c5ac60600bad5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2F130203_e1dd0d9b33637f4709c5ac60600bad5c.jpg&h=dc6ecb42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/19/130204_4cf0f0c4ceac8b2bf1f8a8642a28cb60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2F130204_4cf0f0c4ceac8b2bf1f8a8642a28cb60.jpg&h=793818ca&s